{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shiver is a survival horror game in which a sudden blizzard has enveloped your town, but this isn\u2019t an ordinary storm. Reality itself seems to unravel as you navigate a frozen hellscape to find your missing sister \u2013 all while defending yourself not only from horrors beyond our understanding but nature itself. Solve environmental puzzles, combat ice-covered nightmares, and attempt to uncover the mysteries that lie at the eye of the storm, but most importantly\u2026 survive. <br><br><strong>Navigate harsh weather</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Monsters aren\u2019t the only dangers in Shiver\u2026 The weather and inhospitable environments require careful preparation if you hope to survive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330890/extras/GIF2.gif?t=1734395460\" />   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Experience a deep and emotional narrative</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You play as Hannah, a young woman trapped in the middle of a freak blizzard trying to find her lost sister and get her to safety. Where have these creatures come from and what other mysteries will you discover? What fears would you face to save your family?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330890/extras/GIF3.gif?t=1734395460\" />   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Face abhorrent monsters throughout your journey</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Use melee weapons and various firearms to combat the horrifying creatures that seem to come from the ice itself.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330890/extras/GIF4.gif?t=1734395460\" />   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">   <strong>3rd Person Camera</stron